{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"4c03083d-5978-4f88-afe2-aa4d236a03ae","content":"Your `.testsettings` file has three things to migrate:\n\n1. **Test timeout** (30s)\n2. **Code coverage data collector**\n3. **Assembly resolution / deployment**\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` is no longer supported — everything moves to a **`.runsettings`** file. Here's the migration:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01D7m2VVoUffVgPXtRjAE1NQ","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01BgapdHZSFkfvhgiQjU3YGh","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-0a16073b57844997b477064b013cdb42/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <!-- Replaces <Properties><Property name=\"TestTimeout\" value=\"30000\" /></Properties> -->\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>false</DeploymentEnabled>\n  </MSTest>\n\n  <!-- Replaces <AgentRule><DataCollectors>...</DataCollectors></AgentRule> -->\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-0a16073b57844997b477064b013cdb42/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"cc15ff7e-7aa5-4976-aae0-c745efa2534a","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Assembly resolution / test deployment settings\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are no longer supported. The configuration needs to be migrated to a `.runsettings` file and/or MSTest attributes/properties.\n\nLet me provide guidance on how to migrate each setting:\n\n1. **Test timeout**: In MSTest v3, you can set this via `[Timeout]` attribute on individual tests, or globally via `.runsettings` with `<TestTimeout>` under `<MSTest>` section.\n\n\n2. **Code coverage data collector**: This goes into a `.runsettings` file under `<DataCollectors>`.\n3. **Assembly resolution / deployment**: In MSTest v3, deployment is handled differently. The `<DeploymentEnabled>` and related settings go in `.runsettings` under `<MSTest>`.\n\nNow I'll create a `.runsettings` file that consolidates all these settings.","outputTokens":736,"requestId":"2419:2C774B:41DC15:46AD2F:6A031072"},"id":"515bbb87-6f89-484e-8ff4-0ef556742584","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:35:28.061Z","parentId":"f00d59a6-6a82-4be4-9a95-3e4a6b07101d"}
